    <url>/2022/10/09/layout%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9Aedge%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="layout实例：edge浏览器界面"><a href="#layout实例：edge浏览器界面" class="headerlink" title="layout实例：edge浏览器界面"></a>layout实例：edge浏览器界面</h1><p>软件实际界面：</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/CNmYQWMbl6tgs1k.png" alt="image-20220508005256086" style="zoom:25%;" /><p>实现界面：</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/mrHwkVbxKghpMfu.png" alt="image-20220508005457503" style="zoom: 50%;" /><h1 id="中间的logo："><a href="#中间的logo：" class="headerlink" title="中间的logo："></a>中间的logo：</h1><blockquote><p>图片以及矢量图的获取来自：<a href="https://www.iconfont.cn/">iconfont-阿里巴巴矢量图标库</a></p></blockquote><p>太简单了 直接上</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@+id/logo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintHeight_percent</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.08&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintDimensionRatio</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1:1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintLeft_toLeftOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintRight_toRightOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintVertical_bias</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.4&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintHorizontal_bias</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.2&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:background</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@drawable/microsoft&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">TextView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintHeight_percent</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.08&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintWidth_percent</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.5&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@id/logo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@id/logo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintLeft_toRightOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@id/logo&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintRight_toRightOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintHorizontal_bias</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.08&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:text</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Microsoft&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:gravity</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;center&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:textSize</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;45sp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:textStyle</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;bold&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:textColor</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#707070&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/sblyS3qHeO9DULm.png" alt="image-20220508012803681" style="zoom:50%;" /><h1 id="输入框："><a href="#输入框：" class="headerlink" title="输入框："></a>输入框：</h1><h2 id="VIewGroup使用"><a href="#VIewGroup使用" class="headerlink" title="VIewGroup使用"></a>VIewGroup使用</h2><h3 id="ViewGroup选择"><a href="#ViewGroup选择" class="headerlink" title="ViewGroup选择"></a>ViewGroup选择</h3><p>先观察，有三个控件：<code>edittext</code>，<code>imageVIew</code>(QRcode)，<code>imageView</code>(microphone)</p><p>从左至右排列，使用<code>LinearLayout</code></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">LinearLayout</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintWidth_percent</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.74&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintHeight_percent</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.07&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintLeft_toLeftOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintRight_toRightOf</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;parent&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">app:layout_constraintVertical_bias</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0.75&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">EditText</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">            <span class="hljs-attr">android:id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@+id/input&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">            <span class="hljs-attr">android:id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@+id/QRCode&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">            <span class="hljs-attr">android:id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@+id/microphone&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">LinearLayout</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="ViewGroup的背景"><a href="#ViewGroup的背景" class="headerlink" title="ViewGroup的背景"></a>ViewGroup的背景</h3><p>背景是一个椭圆形<br>这里我们就要创建一个 drawable 作为它的 background</p><p>（ 见另一篇 《shape的使用》）</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml">res/drawable/input_box.xml<br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">shape</span> <span class="hljs-attr">xmlns:android</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">corners</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:radius</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;100dp&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">solid</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@color/white&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">shape</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/EhuSPLaoeU5Idyx.png" alt="image-20220508015425647"></p><p>是不是还差点意思？对，阴影<br>VIew有一个高度的属性：<code>elevation</code></p><blockquote><p>elevation : n. 高度，海拔</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">LinearLayout</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">        <span class="hljs-attr">android:elevation</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;10dp&quot;</span> &gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/2nCIaBuj4H1cQyo.png" alt="image-20220508015833939"></p><h2 id="VIew使用"><a href="#VIew使用" class="headerlink" title="VIew使用"></a>VIew使用</h2><p>接下来写这三个控件：</p><h3 id="View的大小（LinearLayout的weight方法）"><a href="#View的大小（LinearLayout的weight方法）" class="headerlink" title="View的大小（LinearLayout的weight方法）"></a>View的大小（LinearLayout的weight方法）</h3><p>首先是大小，我们采用LinearLayout独有的方法 权重<code>weight</code>:</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">EditText</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          <span class="hljs-attr">android:id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@+id/input&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_weight</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;5&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;match_parent&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@+id/QRCode&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_weight</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;match_parent&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@+id/microphone&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_weight</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0dp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">           <span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;match_parent&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="EditText的使用"><a href="#EditText的使用" class="headerlink" title="EditText的使用"></a>EditText的使用</h3><h4 id="提示语的编辑"><a href="#提示语的编辑" class="headerlink" title="提示语的编辑"></a>提示语的编辑</h4><p><code>hint</code>属性：hint 、 hintcolor ···</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">EditText</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          <span class="hljs-attr">android:textSize</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;20sp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          <span class="hljs-attr">android:hint</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;搜索或键入web地址&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/jVleOCvFJqAnUhP.png" alt="image-20220508020350054" style="zoom:150%;" /><h4 id="下划线"><a href="#下划线" class="headerlink" title="下划线"></a>下划线</h4><p>我们不要这个下划线,加上这一句</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">EditText</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">android:background</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@null&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/9EoVPnKiv1uHGdf.png" alt="image-20220508020657368" style="zoom:150%;" /><h4 id="光标-cursor"><a href="#光标-cursor" class="headerlink" title="光标 cursor"></a>光标 cursor</h4><p>跑起来的光标是丑丑的荧光原谅色 哒咩！</p><img src="C:\Users\Lenovo\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220508020801455.png" alt="image-20220508020801455" style="zoom:80%;" /><p>我们为光标新建一个drawable</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml">res/drawable/cursor.xml<br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">shape</span> <span class="hljs-attr">xmlns:android</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">size</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;2dp&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">solid</span> <span class="hljs-attr">android:color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@android:color/darker_gray&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">shape</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后调用 <code>text Cursor Drawable</code></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">EditText</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">          <span class="hljs-attr">android:textCursorDrawable</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@drawable/cursor&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/TsG4eaRxibIo76V.png" alt="image-20220508021431482"></p><h4 id="取消界面自动聚焦EditText"><a href="#取消界面自动聚焦EditText" class="headerlink" title="取消界面自动聚焦EditText"></a>取消界面自动聚焦EditText</h4><p>有的机子运行界面，发现会自动弹出键盘<br>这是因为界面会自动聚焦到editText上<br>在父布局里加上以下代码<br>可以让父布局夺取焦点</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">androidx.constraintlayout.widget.ConstraintLayout</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:focusable</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:focusableInTouchMode</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="ImageView"><a href="#ImageView" class="headerlink" title="ImageView"></a>ImageView</h3><p>为 两个imageview添加 <u><em><code>background </code></em></u><br>会发现图片极其怪异</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">         ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">android:background</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@drawable/qr_code&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">         ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">android:background</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@drawable/microphone&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/oXcqrINySObma2n.png" alt="image-20220508022153298" style="zoom:150%;" /><p>这是因为 background 会自动拉伸填满控件<br>view还有一个可以添加背景的属性 <code>src</code></p><p>（见另一篇 《background 和 src 》）</p><p>background会根据ImageView组件给定的长宽进行拉伸，而src就存放的是原图的大小，不会进行拉伸。src是图片内容(前景)，bg是背景，可以同时使用。</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">         ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">android:src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@drawable/qr_code&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">         ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">android:src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;@drawable/microphone&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/Lmc8a2zpJHtMgxu.png" alt="image-20220508022759546" style="zoom:150%;" /><p>好多了，但是有点大</p><p>给两个imageView加上margin</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">         ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_marginVertical</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;10dp&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ImageView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">         ···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">android:layout_marginVertical</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;10dp&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/m5tqzHkQxWMOY2A.png" alt="image-20220508023959252" style="zoom:150%;" /><p>这样就差不多了</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/RW9swOZgXfvxLK2.png" alt="image-20220508024322910"></p><p>但是，如果这时候横过屏来</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/rXGSyWtH8eFZwcD.png" alt="image-20220508024448314"></p><h3 id="TextView自动调整text大小"><a href="#TextView自动调整text大小" class="headerlink" title="TextView自动调整text大小"></a>TextView自动调整text大小</h3><p>字体就会出现一些奇怪的事情，我们需要让字体去适应他的TextVIew</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">TextView</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">···</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:autoSizeTextType</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;uniform&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:autoSizeMinTextSize</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;10sp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:autoSizeMaxTextSize</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;50sp&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag">    <span class="hljs-attr">android:autoSizeStepGranularity</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;2sp&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>android:autoSizeTextType&#x3D;”uniform”</p><blockquote><p>使用自动调整</p></blockquote><p>android:autoSizeMinTextSize&#x3D;”10sp”<br>android:autoSizeMaxTextSize&#x3D;”50sp”</p><blockquote><p>设置字体最大最小尺寸</p></blockquote><p>android:autoSizeStepGranularity&#x3D;”2sp”</p><blockquote><p>设置粒度，即字体每次放大缩小的尺寸</p><p>例如这里粒度设置为2sp，若原始为10sp，下一次放大会变成12sp，14sp····</p></blockquote><p>好多了</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/05/08/HVrxQihz4LEWfSm.png" alt="image-20220508030159583"></p><p>（其实横屏的话应该再写一个layout布局，这里只是为了引出textView的自动调整）</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
